Extra Improved Damage = 1120 * 0.20 = 224<br>
Extra Crit Damage = 1120 * 0.50 = 560<br>
--------------------------------------------<br>
Total Damage = 1120 + 224 + 560 = 1904<br>
<br>
Thus, the maximum crit with maximum Improved Damage is 1904 points of damage.  (Note that this uses a max of 50% extra damage for a crit, which is the commonly held belief.)<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
